-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                             ==== README ====

                               -- wxCron --
                              Version 0.2.0
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

DESCRIPTION
~~~~~~~~~~~
WxCron is a cron-like job scheduler.
It is a clone of the good old cron (aka Vixie Cron) and anacron and is full
plattform independent.

LICENSE
